      "settings": {
        "full_width": true,
        "remove_vertical_spacing": true,
        "remove_horizontal_spacing": true,
        "liquid": "<div class=\"expect-section\">\n\n  <h2 class=\"expect-title\">What To Expect</h2>\n\n  <div class=\"expect-card\">\n    <p class=\"expect-tag\">DAY 1</p>\n    <h3 class=\"expect-card-title\">Immediate relief</h3>\n    <p class=\"expect-card-body\">No wire digging into your ribs. No pressure points. Your shoulders drop and the all-day adjusting finally stops.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"expect-card\">\n    <p class=\"expect-tag\">WEEK 1–2</p>\n    <h3 class=\"expect-card-title\">You stop thinking about it</h3>\n    <p class=\"expect-card-body\">The CradleBand™ carries the weight from below — so your neck and shoulders do nothing. You get to 4pm and realize you haven't touched your bra once.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"expect-card\">\n    <p class=\"expect-tag\">WEEK 3–4</p>\n    <h3 class=\"expect-card-title\">Your clothes fit differently</h3>\n    <p class=\"expect-card-body\">Natural lift, natural separation. The tops you stopped wearing start coming back out of the closet.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"expect-card\">\n    <p class=\"expect-tag\">MONTH 2+</p>\n    <h3 class=\"expect-card-title\">You can't go back</h3>\n    <p class=\"expect-card-body\">Women tell us the same thing: they tried wearing their old bra for a day just to check. They sent it back within the hour.</p>\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n\n<style>\n.expect-section {\n  background: #ffffff;\n  padding: 40px 20px;\n  max-width: 680px;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n}\n\n.expect-title {\n  font-size: clamp(24px, 5vw, 32px);\n  font-weight: 800;\n  color: #1a1a1a;\n  text-align: center;\n  margin-bottom: 28px;\n}\n\n.expect-card {\n  background: #f9f5f2;\n  border-radius: 14px;\n  padding: 24px 22px;\n  margin-bottom: 14px;\n}\n\n.expect-tag {\n  font-size: 12px;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  color: #C4614A;\n  text-transform: uppercase;\n  letter-spacing: 0.08em;\n  margin-bottom: 8px;\n}\n\n.expect-card-title {\n  font-size: 20px;\n  font-weight: 700;\n  color: #1a1a1a;\n  margin-bottom: 10px;\n  line-height: 1.3;\n}\n\n.expect-card-body {\n  font-size: 14px;\n  color: #666;\n  line-height: 1.65;\n  margin: 0;\n}\n\n@media (max-width: 480px) {\n  .expect-section { padding: 32px 16px; }\n  .expect-card { padding: 18px 16px; }\n}\n</style>",
