            "content": "<p>Most winter boots lose grip when temperatures drop. The rubber hardens. You slip even in \"winter boots.\"</p><p>ELORYA's sole stays flexible in sub-zero temps. Aggressive tread bites into ice. Grip holds even when wet.</p><p>2,000+ customers tested them. Most feel stable from step one.</p><p><strong>30-day guarantee. Don't like them? Full refund.</strong></p>",
            "link_text": "",
            "link_url": "",
            "background": "#ffffff",
            "background_gradient": "",
            "text_color": "#1a1a1a",
            "text_gradient": "",
            "button_background": "",
