    "testimonials_gcYEBK": {
      "type": "testimonials",
      "blocks": {
        "testimonial_znRQxA": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "round_avatar": true,
            "show_rating": true,
            "rating": 5,
            "author": "",
            "title": "01-28-2026 · Michael T",
            "content": "<p>Been wearing these for 3 weeks now in Chicago. Walk my dog twice a day, rain or snow. My old Columbias would leave my feet frozen after 20 minutes. These? Warm the entire walk. The wide toe box is a game-changer - no more cramped toes. Worth every penny.</p>"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_UGQYqW": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "round_avatar": true,
            "show_rating": true,
            "rating": 5,
            "author": "",
            "title": "01-25-2026 · Sarah K.",
            "content": "<p>Bought these after slipping on my driveway and nearly breaking my wrist. The grip is NO JOKE. Walked on pure ice yesterday and felt completely stable. First winter boots that actually deliver on the non-slip promise.</p>"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_FXDEwy": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "round_avatar": true,
            "show_rating": true,
            "rating": 5,
            "author": "",
            "title": "01-22-2026 · James R.",
            "content": "<p>I work construction in Minnesota. On my feet 10+ hours in the cold. These boots keep my feet warm AND comfortable all day. No break-in period needed. Just put them on and they felt great from day one.</p>"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_QLjQpD": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "round_avatar": true,
            "show_rating": true,
            "rating": 5,
            "author": "",
            "title": "01-16-2026 · Linda M",
            "content": "<p>Got these for my husband (72) after he kept complaining about his old boots being too tight. He says the wide fit is \"like heaven\" and he can actually feel his toes again. He wears them every single day now. Best gift I've gotten him in years.</p>"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_3dWeLp": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "round_avatar": true,
            "show_rating": true,
            "rating": 5,
            "author": "",
            "title": "01-16-2026 · David H.",
            "content": "<p>Skeptical at first - tried so many \"winter boots\" that failed. But these are different. Sole stays flexible in the cold. Grip on ice is solid. Feet stay dry even after hours outside. Finally found boots that work.</p>"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_bB89eU": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "round_avatar": true,
            "show_rating": true,
            "rating": 5,
            "author": "",
            "title": "01-12-2026 · Karen W.",
            "content": "<p>Commute to work on foot every day. These boots are lighter than my old ones but just as warm. Love that I don't look like I'm heading to the Arctic either - they're actually stylish enough for the office.</p>"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_6CqNny": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "round_avatar": true,
            "show_rating": true,
            "rating": 4,
            "author": "",
            "title": "01-10-2026 · Robert G.",
            "content": "<p>Walk 3 miles every morning, no matter the weather. My feet used to be numb halfway through. Not anymore. Warm from start to finish. The traction on icy sidewalks is excellent too.</p>"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_Y3UXYY": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "round_avatar": true,
            "show_rating": true,
            "rating": 4,
            "author": "",
            "title": "01-08-2026 · Jennifer L.",
            "content": "<p>Customer service was great when I had questions about sizing. Boots arrived fast and fit perfectly. Warm, waterproof, comfortable. Everything they promised.</p>"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_HCWEMd": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "round_avatar": true,
            "show_rating": true,
            "rating": 5,
            "author": "",
            "title": "01-05-2026 · Tom S.",
            "content": "<p>Finally, boots that don't squeeze my feet. The wide toe box makes all the difference. Wore them shoveling snow for 2 hours - feet stayed warm and dry. Highly recommend.</p>"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_BMwFVa": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "round_avatar": true,
            "show_rating": true,
            "rating": 5,
            "author": "",
            "title": "01-03-2026 · Patricia D.",
            "content": "<p>Bought for my mom. She can put them on herself without help, which is huge for her independence. She says they're the most comfortable winter boots she's ever owned.</p>"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_iMfLKg": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
